name: DARK CRYSTAL
description:
“The dark crystal” was inspired by one of my favorite fantasy films. This stunning necklace is handmade using real Onyx and Hematite gemstones. Black is the color of elegance and is versatile. Each crystal was carefully hand strung into place with silk thread, a true technique that takes hours to complete. 

Onyx can help release negative emotions such as sorrow and grief it is known to defend against negativity that is directed at you. Hematite brings a quality of energy that is powerful it works with ones mind by calming it and clearing unnecessary negative energy.

Please feel free to message me with any questions regarding this item

name: GREAT EXPECTATIONS
description:
Great expectations was inspired by all the shades of green used in one of my favorite movies so be ready to expect a whole bunch of compliments. This stunning necklace is handmade using real Turquoise "friendship stone", Malachite "relationship stone" and Fresh water pearls. 

Turquoise is one of the oldest protection amulets, and was also known as a symbol of wealth in many ancient cultures. If given a turquoise by a loving friend, that stone would protect the wearer from negative energy and bring good fortune.

Malachite is said to protect the wearer from accidents and protects travelers. Malachite has been used to aid success in business and protect against undesirable associations.

Each crystal was carefully hand strung into place with silk thread, a true technique that takes hours to complete. 


Please feel free to message me with any questions regarding this item

name: MYKONOS MERMAID
description:
A mermaid can never have too many pearls! Inspired by my trip to the island of Mykonos this stunning handmade jewelry piece composed of genuine cultured fresh water pearls 7-8mm, Each pearl is carefully hand strung into place with silk thread, in a true vintage technique that takes hours to complete.

I have designed this necklace with 3 strands and added peek a boo silver skulls. This necklace is truly unique and elegant it can be worn sideways.

Please feel free to email me if you have any questions about this piece
